import React, { useState } from 'react'; import Axios from 'axios'; function ApplicantForm() { const url="http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/apply/"; const [data,setData]=useState({ Name:"", FName:"Sar", Gender:"Male", DOB:"2002-04-04", Age:"18", Category:"ABC", Ward:"EKV", SubDistrict:"Erode", District:"Erode", State:"Tamilnadu", Pincode:"123456", Mobile:"9087654321", AadharNo:"123456789012", Disablity:"No", DisabilityType:"None", BPL_Family_ID:"ded", BankDetails:"Nothin", IGNOAPS:"Yes", IGNWPS:"Yes", IGNDPS:"Yes", NFBS:"Yes" }) function submit(e) { e.preventDefault(); Axios.post(url,{ Name:"Kanishka", "FName":"Sar", "Gender":"Male", "DOB":"2002-04-04", "Age":18, "Category":"ABC", "Ward":"EKV", "SubDistrict":"Erode", "District":"Erode", "State":"Tamilnadu", "Pincode":123456, "Mobile":9087654321, "AadharNo":123456789012, "Disablity":"No", "DisabilityType":"None", "BPL_Family_ID":"ded", "BankDetails":"Nothin", "IGNOAPS":"Yes", "IGNWPS":"Yes", "IGNDPS":"Yes", "NFBS":"Yes" }).then(res=>{ console.log(res.data); }) } function handle(e) { const newdata=(...data)=> newdata[e.target.id]=e.target.value setData(newdata) console.log(newdata) } return(
submit(e)}> handle(e)} id="Name" value={data.Name} placeholder='Name' type="text"> handle(e)} id="Fname" value={data.FName} placeholder='Fname' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Gender" value={data.Gender} placeholder='Gender' type='text'> handle(e)} id="DOB'" value={data.DOB} placeholder='DOB' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Age" value={data.Age} placeholder='Age' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Category" value={data.Category} placeholder='Category' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Ward" value={data.Ward} placeholder='Ward' type='text'> handle(e)} id="SubDistrict" value={data.SubDistrict} placeholder='SubDistrict' type='text'> handle(e)} id="District" value={data.District} placeholder='District' type='text'> handle(e)} id="State" value={data.State} placeholder='State' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Pincode" value={data.Pincode} placeholder='Pincode' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Mobile" value={data.Mobile} placeholder='Mobile' type='number'> handle(e)} id="AadharNo" value={data.AadharNo} placeholder='AadharNo' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Disability" value={data.Disablity} placeholder='Disability' type='text'> handle(e)} id="DisabilityType" value={data.DisabilityType} placeholder='DisabilityType' type='text'> handle(e)} id="BPL_Family_ID" value={data.BPL_Family_ID} placeholder='BPL_Family_ID' type='text'> handle(e)} id="BankDetails" value={data.BankDetails} placeholder='BankDetails' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNOAPS" value={data.IGNOAPS} placeholder='IGNOAPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNWPS" value={data.IGNWPS} placeholder='IGNWPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNDPS" value={data.IGNDPS} placeholder='IGNDPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="NFBS" value={data.NFBS} placeholder='NFBS' type='text'>
); } export default ApplicantForm;
